These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Sport: cricket, skiing, weightlifting
1. Sport:skiing is on the right of Sport:weightlifting##1
2. Sport:cricket is on the far right##1
3. Sport:cricket is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | weightlifting | skiing | cricket |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Food: asparagus, onion, strawberry
1. Food:onion is in an odd position##4
2. Food:asparagus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | asparagus | strawberry | onion |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Hobby: filmmaking, video-games, fishing
1. Hobby:video-games is in an even position##4
2. Hobby:video-games is on the left or right of Hobby:fishing##3
3. Hobby:fishing is on the right of Hobby:video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | video-games | fishing |

 #################################
 
